      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding weekend project or a budget-friendly way to get into a classic frame? This vehicle is ready for a dedicated owner with a vision! While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to return to its former glory, it offers a fantastic foundation for someone who loves to roll up their sleeves. It\u2019s an honest car with plenty of potential for the right person!",
