      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, which remains in superlative, showroom-grade condition. Meticulously preserved and exhibiting no signs of wear, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands absolute perfection. From its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments, every detail reflects an extraordinary standard of care. This is a definitive example of the model, offering an unparalleled driving experience for those who accept only the finest automotive standards.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
